</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Hyundai 全新客貨車 Staria   劃時代外形 + 安全性更高</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/12/2022-hyundai-staria-van/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=2022-hyundai-staria-van</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 12 Mar 2022 07:20:24 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[hyundai]]></category><category><![CDATA[Hyundai Staria Van]]></category><category><![CDATA[現代汽車]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089926</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>香港現代汽車（Hyundai HK）近日推出全新的柴油客貨車 Staria，其型號名稱由「Star」（星星）及 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">香港現代汽車（Hyundai HK）近日推出全新的柴油客貨車 Staria，其型號名稱由「Star」（星星）及「Ria」（波浪）結合而成，車身內外都充滿科幻設計。與以往推出的 H1 Van 相比，Staria 的體積及空間均較廣闊，闊度及高度近 2 米；標準版車價為港幣 278,800 元起。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0009.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089939" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0009-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0009-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0009-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0009.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0015.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089943" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0015-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0015-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0015-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0015.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0011.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0011-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0011-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0011-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0011.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">廠方展出黑色的 LUX 版本 Staria</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Hyundai Staria Van 車身比 H1 長了 103 mm 至 5,253mm，軸距長達 3,273mm。載貨空間相比 H1 多了 379 公升至 2,890 公升，尾箱長度達 1.6 米，最高負載重量達 1,000kg。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0003-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089948" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0003-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0003-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0003-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0003-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Hyundai Staria Van 標準版 6 座配備原廠皮革座椅，設有 4.2 吋 TFT 懸浮式數碼表板；中控台有一部 8 吋的觸控屏幕，可支持 CarPlay 功能，另外還有 Qi 無綫手機充電板、前後雙 USB 插座、後泊鏡頭及前後泊車感應器等。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1089953 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/20220304_114429-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/20220304_114429-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/20220304_114429-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/20220304_114429-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/20220304_114429-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/20220304_114429-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/20220304_114429-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0005-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089947" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0005-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0005-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0005-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0005-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">LUX 版本採用按鍵式波箱，廠方透露日後或會追加軚盤轉波撥片，操作更加方便。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0013-rotated.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089941" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0013-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0013-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0013-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0013-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0004-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089946" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0004-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0004-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0004-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0004-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而同場廠方亦展出了不日登場的 Hyundai Staria Van Lux 版本，主要增加了全車 LED 燈包括車頭的位置燈、日行燈、組合頭尾燈、按鍵式轉波系統、主動安全設備、10.25 吋數碼表板、前排冷暖透氣、環迴鏡頭及電動尾門等等，但售價暫時尚未公佈。規格上，Staria Van 用上一台 2.2 公升柴油 Turbo 引擎，最大馬力輸出 177 匹以及 44kgm 扭力，配合 8 速自動波箱及前驅，平均耗油量 8.2L/100km。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0000-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089949" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0000-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0000-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0000-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0000-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0001-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089950" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0001-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0001-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0001-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/unwire0001-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>售價與規格</h2><div class="page" title="Page 1"><div class="section"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p>車身全長 x 全闊 x 全高：5253 x 1997 x 2000mm</p><div class="page" title="Page 1"><div class="section"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><div class="page" title="Page 1"><div class="section"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p>尾箱容量：2,890l</p><div class="page" title="Page 1"><div class="section"><div class="